{"tid":110334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲隔空警告特朗普　若貿易停止戰爭會開始","createTime":"2017-02-06T14:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T15:09:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24f622bc09883568a11d976a00961d9648bed2ba","tid":110334,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"馬雲隔空警告特朗普　　若貿易停止戰爭會開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2017/02/alibaba-ceo-warns-if-trade-stops-war-starts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2017%2F02%2Falibaba-ceo-warns-if-trade-stops-war-starts%2F&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8482f0d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2017/02/alibaba-ceo-warns-if-trade-stops-war-starts/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/jack-ma-alibaba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fjack-ma-alibaba.jpg&h=6db5c090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴CEO馬雲最近去澳洲出席活動時，提到特朗普近來反全球化的傾向。馬雲認為全球化貿易十分重要，並警告若貿易停止，戰爭便會開始。<br />\n<br />\n據英國獨立報報道，馬雲出席阿里巴巴在澳洲和紐西蘭的總部的活動時，稱他知道每個人都關心貿易戰，他認為全球化是必需的，若貿易停止，戰爭便會開始。<br />\n<br />\n不過，馬雲亦認為要多溝通，同意大家需公平公開的貿易條件。事實上，馬雲上曾與特朗普會面，他用上「有趣」去形容。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：World Economic Forum"},{"pid":"9d6ff7ef9dd110a43e17ff5647af876be0849bd6","tid":110334,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"「全球化是未來」 馬雲：貿易中止會發生戰爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/5/2267306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F5%2F2267306&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1bd854de\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/5/2267306</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/01/24/2/3108164.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F2%2F3108164.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=4e843f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬雲2月4日在墨爾本出席阿里巴巴澳洲、紐西蘭分公司成立儀式時表示，如果貿易中止，戰爭將隨之而來。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲表示：「這個世界需要全球化，需要貿易。人人都擔心貿易大戰。如果貿易中止，戰爭將隨即展開。然而擔心無法解決問題。你唯一能做的是，主動介入，證明貿易有助人們相互溝通。我們應該擁有公平、透明且具有包容性的貿易。」<br />\n<br />\n馬雲又說，「全球化是未來」，「貿易與信任、文化交流有關」。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普上個月20日就職後，立刻簽署行政命令，讓美國退出跨太平洋夥伴協定（TPP）。特朗普曾說，TPP很可能對美國造成嚴重傷害，他將改變對策，轉而與各國「協商公平的雙邊貿易協定」，俾為美國人民帶來就業機會，「重振工業」。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲上個月10日在紐約會晤當時尚未就職的特朗普時表示，阿里巴巴將協助川普政府，在美國創造100萬個就業機會。"},{"pid":"d535bfc5ef6a1244938c43b08c89aef76f869f4f","tid":110334,"uid":18445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"你大我呀. jpg"},{"pid":"6f7fd0884e565476535adeae65c295ca6eb2f214","tid":110334,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"憑乜撚嘢身份咁樣講呀？ 戇撚鳩鳩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7135ac3a67bd5e3da9e0cd3a6acda9672204259c","tid":110334,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"鎖国玩內燒都夠你玩啦"},{"pid":"854ac730b51efabcbe7dee9e6f4959131615b7c3","tid":110334,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"侵想打你好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ce67c8e1b0fb1009ac3338efc41d385efc305d","tid":110334,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱侵侵先同你傾話入美國做生意，到大家搭晒膊頭之後，一個屈尾十就咁樣搞事，馬雲真係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b5bdc6570274775e45892c46ce135e403b8312","tid":110334,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"侵都唔知邊個係馬雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif